#
# This program calculates a 3-term moving average.
#
# Set DPS 3. DEG/RAD is arbitrary.
# Use GOTO 0 0, then press R/S and enter x1, x2, and x3.
# After x3, press R/S to display x_bar1.
# Enter each next value and press R/S again to display the next moving average.
# Example:
#   GOTO 0 0, R/S, 3.4 R/S, 3.3 R/S, 3.5 R/S -> 3.400
#   3.7 R/S -> 3.500
#   3.6 R/S -> 3.600
#   3.6 R/S -> 3.633
#   3.9 R/S -> 3.700
#   4.1 R/S -> 3.867
#
